  "notes": "Wife of Andrew 'Pop' Gemeny. Born in Washington DC. Lived with her parents in DC through the 1920s. Father William Wallace Gordon died June 23, 1926. Married Andrew Gemeny on May 18, 1929 at an Episcopal Church in New York. One son: William Gordon Gemeny (1930). Mother Mary Esther Mayes died April 25, 1957. Died July 23, 1967 in College Park, MD at age 70. Buried in Suitland, MD."
